{"id":209508,"date":[{"year":1950,"month":12,"day":28}],"page":"7","source":"","region":"","masthead":"","special_issue":"俄语周刊","column":"","genre":"","count":"196","ytitle":"","mtitle":"国语课","ftitle":"","authors":[],"text":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"<IMG alt=请插入2号盘，按F5键刷新后显示本插图！ src=\"D:\\inset\\1950\\12\\50CS070801.JPG\">"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"舒适，宽大的教室里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"早晨一片静寂。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"女学生们在做功课:"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"用黑的在白的上写，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"用白的在黑的上写，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"用钢笔和粉笔写:"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“我们不需要"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"战争”。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"建设在斯大林格勒进行着"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们的莫斯科在建设着。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在黑板和练习簿上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"学生们写着字。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在晨光下"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"每一个字母都清晰可见，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"苏联的儿童们写:"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——给全世界人民以和平。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们不需要"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"战争!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"给全世界人民以和平。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在宇宙上每个人都有广阔自由，——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"世界既富足而又伟大。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们苏联的儿童"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这样学习着语言。"}]}